General.Name: Diatreme Resources Ltd
General.Description: Diatreme Resources Limited engages in the exploration of heavy mineral sands, copper, gold, and base metals in Australia. Its flagship property is the Galalar Silica Sand project located in North Queensland. The company was incorporated in 1993 and is based in Coorparoo, Australia.
